420
00:24:35,836 --> 00:24:37,167
I'm not part time, I'm full time.

421
00:24:37,304 --> 00:24:39,169
It's just slow right now.

422
00:24:39,306 --> 00:24:40,000
Sure, 

423
00:24:40,140 --> 00:24:43,803
but your coverage is based on hours worked.

424
00:24:43,944 --> 00:24:46,412
Like I said, you only qualify for second tier.

425
00:24:46,547 --> 00:24:49,380
That has a maximum payout limit of $20,000.

426
00:24:49,516 --> 00:24:50,574
What?

427
00:24:53,420 --> 00:24:55,581
You have been taking money out of my cheque every week.

428
00:24:55,723 --> 00:24:57,623
I've been paying into this policy for years.

429
00:24:58,659 --> 00:25:01,219
That's why we're going to cover you for the full $20,000.

430
00:25:03,230 --> 00:25:05,357
You're kidding me, right? Come on.

431
00:25:06,867 --> 00:25:10,826
You have dropped me from full time to part time. 

432
00:25:10,971 --> 00:25:12,302
You switched carriers.

433
00:25:12,439 --> 00:25:14,771
Now you're telling me I'm not fully covered

434
00:25:14,908 --> 00:25:17,604
