435
00:25:19,279 --> 00:25:20,246
It doesn't seem right, does it?

436
00:25:20,381 --> 00:25:21,370
No, it doesn't. 

437
00:25:21,515 --> 00:25:22,982
My son is very sick.

438
00:25:23,250 --> 00:25:25,081
If I'm not covered, I got a serious problem.

439
00:25:25,219 --> 00:25:28,677
I understand that, but there's nothing I can do.

440
00:25:28,822 --> 00:25:30,687
You can file an appeal.

441
00:25:30,824 --> 00:25:31,654
Yeah?

442
00:25:31,925 --> 00:25:32,892
Here you go. 

443
00:25:33,394 --> 00:25:35,624
That takes about seven working days.

444
