446
00:25:57,184 --> 00:25:58,151
You on welfare?

447
00:25:59,887 --> 00:26:01,286
You should be on welfare.

448
00:26:01,422 --> 00:26:03,219
We both have jobs.

449
00:26:03,357 --> 00:26:04,517
That's too bad.

450
00:26:05,225 --> 00:26:07,022
I'm sorry. I can't help you.

451
00:26:07,428 --> 00:26:09,123
Try County Medical.

452
00:26:09,396 --> 00:26:11,921
Yes, ma'am, I need to speak to somebody in Financial Aid.

453
00:26:13,634 --> 00:26:14,965
No, I don't want to hold.

454
00:26:15,202 --> 00:26:17,966
I've been holding for 15 minutes.

455
00:26:19,158 --> 00:26:23,210
We don't have enough money! Should I get another job?

456
00:26:23,310 --> 00:26:24,402
I'm not yelling.

457
00:26:24,545 --> 00:26:25,739
You're yelling in here!

458
00:26:34,054 --> 00:26:34,952
Next, please.

459
00:26:40,227 --> 00:26:42,320
Wrong line. Window 15.

460
00:26:42,563 --> 00:26:43,461
What?

