does all them special investigative reports.

499
00:30:05,766 --> 00:30:08,132
You know the one, the guy with the frigging hair?

500
00:30:08,268 --> 00:30:10,099
Pretty boy. What's his frigging name?

501
00:30:10,237 --> 00:30:10,760
Lampley.

502
00:30:10,904 --> 00:30:12,303
Tuck Lampley.

503
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:14,798
I'll give you $20 for the TV.

504
00:30:15,175 --> 00:30:16,039
It's a colour TV.

505
00:30:16,176 --> 00:30:17,234
$20.

506
00:30:22,282 --> 00:30:23,271
Call him up, Jimmy.

507
00:30:23,417 --> 00:30:26,443
You don't mind if we walk and talk. I'm up to here today.

508
00:30:26,586 --> 00:30:27,518
Not at all.

509
00:30:27,654 --> 00:30:28,848
What can I do you for?

510
00:30:29,256 --> 00:30:31,190
My son Mike, 

511
00:30:31,325 --> 00:30:33,384
he fell into heart failure at this Little League game.

512
00:30:33,527 --> 00:30:36,985
I got full insurance from the job.

513
00:30:37,130 --> 00:30:38,620
Now they're telling me they won't pay.

514
00:30:38,765 --> 00:30:41,256
What about the hospital? Don't they have to cover it?

515
00:30:41,401 --> 00:30:44,234
- That's what I was saying.
