1191
01:03:22,227 --> 01:03:23,888
All right, Steve. You, too.

1192
01:03:24,829 --> 01:03:26,729
Let's go, both of you.

1193
01:03:27,098 --> 01:03:29,396
Thank you. Muchas gracias. Sir.

1194
01:03:31,536 --> 01:03:33,697
- Thank you, Mr Archibald.
- You, too.

1195
01:03:35,040 --> 01:03:36,735
Take care of his ear.

