The gunman has just freed several hostages.

1197
01:03:39,577 --> 01:03:43,172
by members of the crisis team.

1198
01:03:43,315 --> 01:03:46,682
Will the man known as John Q get a heant for his little boy?

1199
01:03:46,818 --> 01:03:50,379
Only time will tell.From Hope Memorial Hospital. I'm Tuck Lampley.

1200
01:03:50,522 --> 01:03:52,683
Is it true an ambulance dropped off

