01:03:55,393 --> 01:03:57,588
He unlocked the door and he let him inside!

1203
01:03:57,729 --> 01:03:59,094
Can you comment?

1204
01:03:59,230 --> 01:04:00,458
The man was critically injured.

1205
01:04:00,598 --> 01:04:02,532
If he hadn't let him in, he would have died.

1206
01:04:02,667 --> 01:04:03,998
Ma'am, are you all right?

