01:06:08,726 --> 01:06:09,818
You know how easy it is to get a gun?

1254
01:06:09,961 --> 01:06:11,895
Five minutes. Gun show.

1255
01:06:12,430 --> 01:06:14,261
I understand your kid is sick, John,

1256
01:06:14,399 --> 01:06:16,924
but what makes him better than me? I got a life, too.

1257
01:06:17,168 --> 01:06:18,499
But you got insurance.

1258
01:06:18,636 --> 01:06:22,128
So what, are you going to shoot me? That's what you're telling the cops.

1259
01:06:22,273 --> 01:06:24,764
If your son doesn't get the very first heart available, 

1260
01:06:24,909 --> 01:06:26,035
we all die.

1261
01:06:27,946 --> 01:06:29,937
How's it going to end, John?

1262
01:06:30,181 --> 01:06:31,409
What's your move?

1263
01:06:32,283 --> 01:06:35,548
I got no moves, okay? I don't know what I'm going to do.

1264
01:06:38,857 --> 01:06:41,155
I'm waiting on a miracle, okay?

1265
01:06:42,360 --> 01:06:44,590
I'm waiting on an act of God.

1266
01:07:12,624 --> 01:07:14,615
Could we have a word with you, please?

1267
01:07:17,695 --> 01:07:19,219
This is all my fault.

1268
01:07:19,364 --> 01:07:21,594
When the hospital told me they were releasing Mikey,

1269
01:07:21,733 --> 01:07:23,633
I called John and yelled at him,

1270
01:07:23,768 --> 01:07:25,998
told him to do something, anything.

1271
01:07:26,137 --> 01:07:28,731
But I never thought...

1272
01:07:28,873 --> 01:07:29,999
I understand.

1273
01:07:30,141 --> 01:07:32,371
Is he a violent man, Mrs Archibald?

1274
01:07:32,610 --> 01:07:37,445
No! He's sweet and gentle.

1275
01:07:37,916 --> 01:07:39,178
He wouldn't hurt a fly.

1276
01:07:39,317 --> 01:07:42,252
That's not what he's saying.

1277
01:07:42,520 --> 01:07:44,920
He's talking about killing people.

1278
01:07:45,056 --> 01:07:49,288
I may be fishing, but has he spent time in the military or anything like that?

1279
01:07:51,396 --> 01:07:52,226
What is this?

1280
01:07:52,363 --> 01:07:53,387
What?

1281
01:07:54,465 --> 01:07:56,365
I see what's going on here.

1282
01:07:58,169 --> 01:08:00,364
