1287
01:08:08,346 --> 01:08:11,804
You cannot use me to build a case against my husband.

1288
01:08:11,950 --> 01:08:14,350
I support him in everything he does.

1289
01:08:14,485 --> 01:08:16,578
I'm on his side, not yours.

1290
01:08:17,488 --> 01:08:19,217
And you don't talk to me!

1291
01:08:21,459 --> 01:08:25,020
