1295
01:08:38,343 --> 01:08:41,403
I've decided to put Michael's name on the recipient list.

1296
01:08:43,181 --> 01:08:45,615
The hospital will pay for everything.

1297
01:08:47,552 --> 01:08:49,213
Really?

1298
01:08:49,454 --> 01:08:50,716
Really.

1299
01:08:52,223 --> 01:08:53,747
Thank you.

