1305
01:09:12,777 --> 01:09:15,610
For a minute, I actually believed you cared.

1306
01:09:28,559 --> 01:09:30,652
We go now to Hope Memorial Hospital. 

1307
01:09:30,795 --> 01:09:32,353
live... Tuck Lampley.

1308
01:09:32,630 --> 01:09:35,497
As you can see. The crowd in front of Hope Memorial is growing.

