1311
01:09:39,470 --> 01:09:41,335
Standing next to me is James Palumbo.

1312
01:09:41,472 --> 01:09:42,905
friend of John Archibald.

1313
01:09:43,341 --> 01:09:46,037
Mr Palumbo. What can you tell us about John Archibald?

1314
01:09:46,944 --> 01:09:48,275
You know.

1315
01:09:49,514 --> 01:09:52,278
I got to be honest. Tuck.

1316
01:09:52,817 --> 01:09:56,082
This whole thing sucks.

1317
01:09:56,954 --> 01:10:00,446
